chapterDetailsSmall: Google Developers Group Setif is an initiative to concentrate the efforts of many developers in and around Setif to learn, share and get productive using the various Google products.
chapterDescription: Google Developer Group Setif is inspired by GDG Family . We started our journey in July 2017. We try to engage student developers, fresh graduates and professionals through our hack events & meetups. The motive is to create a local ecosystem of programmers & hackers in and around Setif. The technology awareness is main goal for first few years of the group.
